faqList.a10:
If it still hasn't arrived, please provide the following information to contact customer service:
1. Transaction hash (TxID);
2. Deposit amount and time;
3. Screenshots of deposit network and address.

If the deposit fails, please confirm the following information:
1. Whether the deposit address is correct;
2. Whether the selected network is consistent;
3. Whether the blockchain has shown successful transfer (check blockchain explorer).

faqList.a13:
Common reasons include:
1. Incorrect withdrawal address or unsupported chain;
2. Withdrawal amount below minimum withdrawal limit;
3. Insufficient available balance or frozen funds;
4. Abnormal behavior triggered risk control.

Please check if your withdrawal information is correct. If you have any questions, please contact platform customer service.

faqList.a17:
Possible reasons include:
1. Insufficient available balance;
2. Exchange amount below minimum limit or exceeds maximum limit;
3. Network fluctuations caused price refresh, please initiate exchange again.
